description: Up your Friday night dinner with this chicken sausage roll recipe from Clarissa in WA. The whole family will love these crispy, veggie-packed pastries.
name: Chicken & Veg Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 3 sheets reducedfat puff pastry, just thawed

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200°C/180°C fanforced. Line 2 baking trays with baking paper.
Place carrot, zucchini, spinach, mince, potato, herbs, stock powder, Worcestershire sauce and breadcrumbs in a large bowl. Using hands, mix until well combined.
Halve each pastry sheet. Divide mince mixture along centre of pastry pieces. Roll up to enclose filling. Cut each piece into 3 portions. Place sausage rolls, seamsides down, on trays.
Whisk egg and milk in a small bowl. Brush sausage rolls with egg mixture. Bake for 30 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Serve with sauce.
